Starting Norad behaviour analysis from scratch for Yuri in March 2021 CREW script adapted from the Domenech analysis scripts

Data are loaded from a pre-prepared concatenated data file, see the silenced chunks for loading of new data or parameters.

First load the major datafile

First, lets track basic behaviour across sessions?

This script now builds a trial by trial matrix to help the trial analysis, and populates it with the necessary information on each trial and block This allows us to summarise what the monkey(s) are doing within and across blocks.

Under what circumstances do monkeys shift choice?
